- content_for(:title, "Prescription Manager" )
.head-row
  .jumbotron
    %h1 Prescription Manager
    %p 
      You are logged in as 
      = @user.name

%div.welcome-rows
  .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
    .welcome-sections
      %h1 Prescriptions
      = link_to image_tag("prescription.jpg", :id=>'prescrip-main' ,:class=>"img-box"), prescriptions_path, title:"Manage Prescriptions"
      %p Add and view prescriptions & record when they are filled at the pharmacy. Now you can create a new doctor and drug as you create a new prescription.

  .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
    .welcome-sections
      %h1 Drug Library
      = link_to image_tag("drug.jpg", :id=>'drug-main', :class=>"img-box"), drugs_path, title:"Manage Drugs"
      %p Add and view all drugs in your library. These will be added to your prescriptions. You do not need to create these first to create prescriptions.

%div.clearfix

%div.welcome-rows
  .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
    .welcome-sections
      %h1 Pharmacies
      = link_to image_tag("pharmacy.jpg", :id=>'pharmacy-main', :class=>"img-box"), pharmacies_path, title:"Manage your Pharmacies"
      %p Manage your pharmacies. These are used when you fill a prescription.  You do not need to create these first to fill a prescriptions.
  .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
    .welcome-sections
      %h1 Doctor List
      = link_to image_tag("doctor.jpg", id:'doctor-main', :class=>"img-box"), doctors_path, title:"Manage your Doctors"
      %p Manage your doctors. Add new doctors or update them. Used in your prescriptions. You do not need to create these first to create prescriptions.

%div.clearfix

%div.welcome-rows
  .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
    .welcome-sections
      %h1 Manage Costs
      = image_tag("cost.jpg", :class=>"img-box")
      %p Look at your totals for the donut hole and how much you have spent on prescriptions year to date. This is an upcoming feature.


= render 'layouts/nav_footer'